title: Chocolate oatmeal cookie traybake
ingredients: ['225g butter, softened', '220g dark brown soft sugar', '100g caster sugar', '2 eggs', '1/2 teaspoon vanilla extract', '225g plain flour', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '200g porridge oats', '340g plain chocolate chips']
